text: East Side of Heaven is a 1939 American musical movie directed by David Butler and starring Bing Crosby, Joan Blondell, Mischa Auer, Irene Hervey, C. Aubrey Smith, Baby Sandy, Jerome Cowan. It was distributed by Universal Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1939 musical movies Category:1930s American musical movies Category:Movies directed by David Butler Category:Universal Pictures movies
